findings.title: Novel Ketamine Analog Discovery: Ketamine Analog 1
findings.description: Computationally generated analog of Ketamine using  Add Fluorine transformation strategy. Shows very high therapeutic potential with 100% drug-likeness score.
findings.next_steps: Proceed to in vitro receptor binding assays and ADMET profiling
